name: move_three_objects_seed456
description: The robot should move each of the three 0.5m cubed blocks from their starting locations onto the designated platform by pushing them individually.

children.name: walk_to_First_0_5m_cubed_block
children.description: The robot should walk to a position adjacent to the First 0.5m cubed block, preparing to push it. The goal state is for the robot to be within pushing distance of the First 0.5m cubed block, ready for the next pushing action.

children.name: push_First_0_5m_cubed_block_towards_Platform
children.description: The robot should apply continuous force to the First 0.5m cubed block, pushing it from its initial position towards the Platform. The goal state is for the First 0.5m cubed block to be on or very close to the edge of the Platform, ready for final adjustment.

children.name: adjust_First_0_5m_cubed_block_on_Platform
children.description: The robot should make small, controlled pushes to ensure the First 0.5m cubed block is fully and stably positioned within the boundaries of the Platform. The goal state is for the First 0.5m cubed block to be entirely on the Platform, stable and not at risk of falling off.
